message.content:
Upgrade the visual foundation for a professional enterprise asset management system at `/Users/admin/it-asset/`. Style: "fusion" — Linear/Notion modern aesthetic + ServiceNow enterprise functionality.

## 1. GLOBAL CSS — `app/globals.css`

Read the file first, then make these changes:

### Background tint
- `:root`: `--background` change from `oklch(1 0 0)` to `oklch(0.987 0 0)` — subtle gray tint so white cards pop
- `:root`: `--card` stays `oklch(1 0 0)` — cards stay pure white

### Radius
- `--radius` from `0.625rem` to `0.75rem`

### Scrollbar styling
Add at the end of the file in `@layer base`:
```css
/* Custom scrollbar */
::-webkit-scrollbar {
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
}
::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
  background: transparent;
}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
  background: oklch(0 0 0 / 0.15);
  border-radius: 3px;
}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
  background: oklch(0 0 0 / 0.25);
}
.dark ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
  background: oklch(1 0 0 / 0.15);
}
.dark ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
  background: oklch(1 0 0 / 0.25);
}
```

### Selection color
Add in `@layer base`:
```css
::selection {
  background-color: oklch(0.45 0.18 250 / 0.2);
}
```

### Heading tracking
Add in `@layer base`:
```css
h1, h2, h3 { letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
```

### Card shadow token
Add `--shadow-card: 0 1px 3px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 0.06), 0 1px 2px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.06);` to both `:root` and `.dark` blocks. In dark: `--shadow-card: 0 1px 3px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 0.3), 0 1px 2px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.3);`

### Page background subtle pattern
Add `--dot-color: oklch(0 0 0 / 0.03);` to `:root` and `--dot-color: oklch(1 0 0 / 0.03);` to `.dark`. In `@layer base` for `body`:
```css
body::before {
  content: "";
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: -1;
  background-image: radial-gradient(circle, var(--dot-color) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 20px 20px;
}
```
(This gives a very subtle dot grid pattern on the page background)

## 2. CARD COMPONENT — `components/ui/card.tsx`

Read the file first. The Card sub-components need to use shadow instead of just border:

- `Card`: Change from `rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground` to `rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm`. Keep the border for definition against background.
- `Card`: Add `transition-shadow` — interactive cards can use `hover:shadow-md` (but don't add hover to the base Card, that's done by parent pages)

## 3. HEADER — `components/layout/header.tsx`

Read the file first. Add glass-morphism effect:

- Change the header's outer div from `flex h-14 items-center justify-between border-b px-4` to `flex h-14 items-center justify-between border-b bg-background/80 backdrop-blur-md px-4 sticky top-0 z-10`

- For the breadcrumb: make the separator `/` use `text-muted-foreground/40` instead of `text-muted-foreground`

## VERIFICATION
After all edits, run `npx tsc --noEmit` from `/Users/admin/it-asset/` and fix any errors. Then check the file changes look correct.

